The paper discusses the online browsing behavior of Web users, which is a topic related to human-computer interaction (cs.HC). The paper also mentions the optimization of search engines offerings, which falls under information retrieval (cs.IR). The use of social media and networking sites like Facebook or Twitter is related to social computing (cs.SI). The paper also discusses the calculation of website metrics, which is related to software engineering (cs.SD) and natural language processing (cs.CL) as it involves analyzing text data.
